MNN (Mobile Neural Network)
===========================

Project: MNN
Upstream: https://github.com/alibaba/MNN
Version used by LanXin Android: 3.6.0
Packaging: official Android prebuilt shared libraries
  - mnn_3.6.0_android_armv7_armv8_cpu_opencl_vulkan.zip
  - extracted arm64-v8a/*.so into app/src/main/jniLibs/ (build-time download)

License: Apache License 2.0
Full text: https://github.com/alibaba/MNN/blob/master/LICENSE

Copyright: Alibaba Group Holding Limited and MNN contributors.

Notes for LanXin:
- Runtime native libraries (libMNN.so, libMNN_Express.so, libllm.so, optional
  OpenCL/Vulkan/OpenCV/Audio, libc++_shared.so) are downloaded at Gradle build
  time via the `downloadMnnNative` task; they are NOT committed to git.
- Thin JNI wrapper: app/src/main/cpp/mnn_lanxin_jni.cpp → libmnn_lanxin.so
  (headers under third_party/mnn/include/).
- LLM model weights (config.json + *.mnn + tokenizer) are NOT redistributed in
  this repository; users place them under LanXin/models/local-llm/ (see
  docs/local-inference.md).
- x86_64 APK builds use a stub JNI (mnn_lanxin_jni_stub.cpp); real inference
  targets arm64-v8a devices.
